    "body": "What would be a good way to document the css of the widgets? I think that even though v2 is a great upgrade on the doc, I kinda think we failed on the CSS part. Do you have examples of libraries that document their css well? @ronanlevesque @pixelastic @LukyVj @JonasBa ",
