    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "My POV is that it's rather a consistency problem than a doc problem. That being said, I do like the approach taken React IS on its docs, seems clear enough to me (use a table to display the class name and its role inside the component).\r\n\r\nI guess we need to make sure that all our class names follow the same naming conventions in order to make it easier for people to understand what can be modified and its exact role.\r\n\r\nGood news though: it's exactly what I'm working on! :)",
